## Test 4: Lexical Errors
## Tests error detection, reporting, and recovery

## Invalid characters
@
$
~
&
!
=

## Standalone + and - (no digit or duplicate follows)
+a
-b
+
-

## Invalid identifier starts (lowercase not allowed)
count
myVariable
xValue

## Identifier exceeding 31 characters
Abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz012345

## Single # (not a valid comment start)
#
# not a comment

## Float with too many decimal digits (>6)
1.1234567
3.12345678

## Dots and random symbols
.
..
...

## Valid tokens between errors to test recovery
42 @ Count ++ $ true
